text.tspan: If you have any questions about the election
process, please write to us in the form below.
From May 1st to 7th, you can vote for your youth
councillor online at lyac.ca/. After voting, you will
receive a text confirmation that you voted so we
can verify your vote. You can also vote via ballot if
a candidate canvasses you at the door.
